column2: SELECT    m.id as [id], str(m.ra,#,#) AS ra, str(m.dec,#,#) AS dec,  n.distance,    sp.ra AS ra2, sp.dec AS dec2,      dbo.fPhotoTypeN(sp.type) as photo_type,       str(sp.modelMag_u,#,#) as u,str(sp.modelMagErr_u,#,#) as err_u,      str(sp.modelMag_g,#,#) as g,str(sp.modelMagErr_g,#,#) as err_g,      str(sp.modelMag_r,#,#) as r,str(sp.modelMagErr_r,#,#) as err_r,      str(sp.modelMag_i,#,#) as i,str(sp.modelMagErr_i,#,#) as err_i,      str(sp.modelMag_z,#,#) as z,str(sp.modelMagErr_z,#,#) as err_z,   str(pp.z,#,#) as photo_z, po.plate, po.mjd, po.fiberid, str(po.z,#,#) as spec_z into [myscratch:default].out_q_dr1#_#v2_#p5 from MyDB.in_q_dr1#_# AS m      OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS sp ON n.objid=sp.objid     LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecPhoto AS po ON po.objID=sp.objID         LEFT OUTER JOIN photoZ pp ON pp.objID = sp.objID    ORDER by m.id
